    <p><b>GreenRoots Agriculture</b> was <u>founded in 1985</u> by a group of <i>passionate farmers</i> with a vision to revolutionize sustainable farming.</p>

    <p class="info large-text">What started as a small cooperative of <span class="highlight">organic farmers</span> in Iowa has grown into a national leader in eco-friendly agriculture.</p>

    <p class="highlight small-text">Over the decades, our focus has remained on quality, sustainability, and community impact.</p>

